sc_cat_item.description:
Short Description: A royal experience in the land of forts, palaces, and deserts.

Long Description:
Discover Rajasthan’s royal history and desert landscapes. Start in Jaipur, exploring the Amber Fort, Hawa Mahal, and local markets. Visit Jodhpur, the "Blue City," known for Mehrangarh Fort and Umaid Bhawan Palace. Experience the golden sands of Jaisalmer, with camel safaris and visits to the Jaisalmer Fort and Patwon Ki Haveli. End your journey in Udaipur, the "City of Lakes," famous for the Lake Palace, City Palace, and serene boat rides on Lake Pichola. Rajasthan’s hospitality and heritage make this tour unforgettable.

Location: Jaipur, Jodhpur, Jaisalmer, Udaipur

Duration: 8-10 days

Highlights: Amber Fort, camel safari, Lake Pichola
